\c 22
\s Kuchema komunhu akasiiwa naMwari
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba, nenondo yamangwanani. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Mwari wangu, Mwari wangu, mandisiireiko? Munomirireiko kure pakundibatsira, napamashoko okugomba kwangu?
\v 2 Mwari wangu, ndinodana masikati, asi hamupinduri; nousiku, asi handiwani zororo.
\v 3 Asi imwi muri mutsvene, imwi mugere parumbidzo dzaIsraeri.
\v 4 Madzibaba edu akavimba nemi; vakavimba, imwi mukavarwira.
\v 5 Vakachema kwamuri, vakarwirwa; vakavimba nemi, vakasanyadziswa.
\v 6 Asi ini ndiri honye, handizi munhu; ndiri chinhu chinozvidzwa navanhu, chinoshorwa navanhu vese.
\v 7 Vese, vanondiona vanondiseka; vanoshamisa muromo, vanodzungudza misoro, vachiti:
\v 8 Chizviisai kuna Jehovha; iye ngaamurwire; ngaamurwire, zvaanomufarira iye.
\p
\v 9 Asi ndimi makandibudisa pachizvaro; makandivimbisa nemwi ndichiri pamazamu amai vangu.
\v 10 Ndakaiswa kwamuri kubva pachizvaro; imwi muri Mwari wangu kubva padumbu ramai vangu.
\v 11 Regai kuva kure neni; nokuti njodzi iri pedo; nokuti hapana angabatsira.
\v 12 Hondo zhinji dzakandikomba; hondo dzine simba dzaBhashani dzakandipoteredza.
\v 13 Dzinondishamisira miromo yadzo, seshumba inoparadza ichiomba.
\v 14 Ndakadururwa semvura, mafupa angu ese akasvodogoka; moyo wangu wakafanana nenamo; wakanyauka mukati moura hwangu.
\v 15 Simba rangu rakaoma sechaenga; rurimi rwangu rwakanamatira pashaya dzangu; makandiisa paguruva rorufu.
\v 16 Nokuti imbwa dzakandikomberedza; ungano yavanoita zvakaipa yakandipoteredza; vakaboora maoko angu namakumbo angu.
\v 17 Ndingaverenga mafupa angu ese; vanonditarira nokundinananidza.
\v 18 Vanogovana nguvo dzangu pakati pavo, vanokanda mijenya pamusoro pehazu yangu.
\p
\v 19 Asi imwi Jehovha, regai kuva kure neni; imwi simba rangu, kurumidzai kundibatsira.
\v 20 Rwirai mweya wangu pamunondo; mudikanwi wangu pasimba rembwa.
\v 21 Ndiponesei pamuromo weshumba; zvirokwazvo, makandipindura ndiri pakati penyanga dzenyati.
\p
\v 22 Ndichadudzira zita renyu kuhama dzangu; ndichakurumbidzai pakati peungano.
\v 23 Imwi munotya Jehovha, murumbidzei; imwi mese vana vaJakove, mukudzei; mumutyei, imwi mese vana vaIsraeri.
\v 24 Nokuti haana kuzvidza kana kusema dambudziko raanotambudzwa; kana kumuvanzira chiso chake; asi panguva yaakachema kwaari akamunzwa.
\v 25 Kurumbidza kwangu paungano huru kunobva kwamuri; ndicharipa mhiko dzangu pamberi pavanomutya.
\v 26 Vanyoro vachadya vakaguta; vanotsvaka Jehovha ndivo vachamurumbidza; moyo yenyu ngairarame nokusingaperi.
\v 27 Migumo yese yenyika icharangarira nokudzokera kuna Jehovha; marudzi ese avahedheni achanamata kwamuri.
\v 28 Nokuti ushe ndohwaJehovha; ndiye mubati wavahedheni.
\v 29 Vakuru vese venyika vachadya nokunamata; vese vanoburukira kuguruva vachafugama pamberi pake, naiye asingagoni kuraramisa mweya wake.
\v 30 Vana vake vachanamata kwaari; rudzi runotevera ruchaudzwa zvaJehovha.
\v 31 Vachauya vachidudzira kururama kwake kuvanhu vachazozvarwa, kuti ndiye wakazviita.
